<select
  ng-options="cantrip as cantrip for cantrip in ctrl.selectedCharClass.cantrips track by cantrip"
  ng-model="ctrl.classCantrips"
  name="cantrips"
  multiple>
</select>

<p>You also gain the Druidic Language ability, which allows you leave secret messages for other druids. You and others who know this language can automatically spot a message, others can spot it with a successful perception check but can't read it without magic.</p>
